name: My Tiny Alien
description:
My Tiny Alien
  • Simple jumping or tower climber game. 
  • Collect the whites to score
  • Be careful the tiny birds are dangerous.
  • Don't fall to the ground. The red colored enemy will kill you.
  • Use the arrow keys to play the game. 
  • Controls
    • Up Arrow - Jump
    • Left Arrow - Move Left
    • Right Arrow - Move Right
